{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-005__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-005", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-005__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·005.1", "text_original": "蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿伐，召伯所茇。\n蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿敗，召伯所憇。\n蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿拜，召伯所說。", "text_normalized": "蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿伐，召伯所茇。\n蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿敗，召伯所憇。\n蔽芾甘棠，勿翦勿拜，召伯所說。", "notes": "甘棠 Chinese poem 1."}
